    dc:description "Fig. 22. Trochaclis regalisMarshall, 1995,Walters Shoal, stn DW4881 (MNHN). A–C.Apertural, oblique basal and apical views of specimen with persistent shoulder cord, diameter 1.1 mm. D. Protoconch of A, scale bar=100 μm. E–F. Apertural and apical views of specimen with shoulder cord evanescing after first whorl, diameter 1.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10727801/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

